data.description: Wonderful property located near East Galveston Bay with great amenities for boating and fishing enthusiasts. Enjoy water views from the porch and from inside the home. The open floor plan, attached garage, and detached shop provide plenty of space for both practical needs and leisure activities. The home features 2 bedrooms and 1 full bathroom upstairs and a full bathroom and laundry hook ups located downstairs in the spacious 2 car garage. Home is partially furnished. Grab a few things and call this one yours. Located near the local boat ramp and lighted pier.
